name: Medieval Fighter (Chief)
description:
This is a game made in about 7 days, it was made for an extracurricular activity in 6th grade. I made it with my friends, tested it with my friends, and hope you enjoy it too.

None of this would be possible without Scratch, Turbowarp, and Itch.

I made a Google Site if you want to play it that way.
